This is about a scale which has tipped from being heavily IN our favor to being heavily OUT of our favor, the pendulum having swung too far in the other direction.   It's gone too far, and the lack of good class specific, or stats favorable equipment for warriors has put us into a position where we're forced to say &quot;Yes, I realize that this is most suited for a hybrid, but the MT needs the +100HP, and therefore gets&quot;  This is simply wrong, with all of the various loot items out there, modeling a few who's use is limited or who's stats favor a single class would create a much more harmonious (read fun) environment in which to play.   <br>
<br>
Also, a couple of effective aa skills (i.e. Increased Agitation as described above) and some decent melee output on a class who's viability depends on melee solely will hurt no one, and in my view, would make the game much more fun to play.<br>
