<br>
The straight damage caster (the wizard) is hands down, the best.  Manaburn accentuates that fact.<br>
<br>
The straight damage melee (the warrior) is NOT hands down the best.  Warriors have a very marginal edge.  Should that be right?<br>
<br>
Roll up an SK or paladin and hit their AA button.  Look at everything from Arch and Class and then come back and look at warriors.  They get some really ass beating @#%$. We have broken flurry and AE taunt.  I'm very grateful we got that, but come on.  There really needs to be a bit more there.<br>
